<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <h2 style="color: #333; text-align: center;">Password Reset Code</h2>
  <p>Dear {{firstName}},</p>
  <p>You have requested to reset your password for your carRental account.</p>
  <p>Use the following 6-digit code to reset your password:</p>
  
  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; display: inline-block;">
      <h1 style="color: #dc3545; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 8px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">
        {{code}}
      </h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
    Enter this code in the password reset form to complete the process.
  </p>
  
  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
    If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email. 
    This code will expire in 1 hour.
  </p>
  
  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px;">
    Best regards,<br>
    The member
  </p>
</div> 